branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series VFR consists of 5 port pilot solenoid valves with rubber seals and base mounted type manifolds, available in plug-in and non plug-in styles. Port sizes range from 1/8 to 1/2 with Rc(PT), NPTF &amp; G(PF) thread types available. Various options also available.
&lt;/p&gt;

